<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minhas Notas</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Sora:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/notes.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>


    <main class="notes-shell">
        <section class="notes-hero">
            <div>
                <span class="section-tag">Painel pessoal</span>
                <h1>Minhas notas</h1>
                <p>Veja suas anotações em um só lugar, abra rapidamente o que precisa e continue escrevendo sem perder ritmo.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/notes/create" class="new-note-btn">Criar nova nota</a>
        </section>

        <section class="notes-board">
            <div id="notes-container" class="notes-grid"></div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/notes.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
